title: A Secret Coup Against President Trump? - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/15/17

description:
George Noory and former consultant to President Clinton Dick Morris discuss the progress of President Trump's administration so far, and whether there is a secret plan by his political opponents to wreck his presidency and get him out of office.
